1. *Nemamo* nikakav izbor. (We have no choice.)
2. *Nemamo* vremena za tako nešto. (We don't have time for that.)
3. *Nemamo* nikoga da nam pomogne. (We don't have anyone to help us.)
4. Oni *nemaju* ništa da nam ponude. (They have nothing to offer us.)
5. Oni *nemaju* nikakve veze sa tim. (They have nothing to do with it.)
6. *Nemamo* nijedan dokaz. (We don't have any evidence.)
7. *Nemamo* nikakvih razloga da sumnjamo. (We have no reason to doubt.)
8. *Nemamo* nikakvu nadu. (We have no hope.)